result.title: some problems' time limitation is smaller then even printing out the result
result.content:
Hi:

for example http://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/379/C the output can be 300000 numbers each 9 digits. (test 5) I have tried to print such a line of numbers (using java or scala) even that takes 12 seconds, but the limitation is only 3 seconds. Do you guys see such an issue? Thanks

CY
